folder: Herkimer Street & Rockaway Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Herkimer Street, north side, between Rockaway Ave., and Eastern Parkway, showing the Church of God -- -- Jesus (Italian), at No. 1325. In 1929 it was the Bleecker Memorial Congregational Church. To the right is P.S. No. 155.

April 20, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
